  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Medical treatment for acute appendicitis&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patients with clinically and radiologically approved acute appendicitis will be treated&#xD;
      medically. The main aim of the study is to define the long term results of medical treatment&#xD;
      for acute appendicitis. Patients will be followed by clinical visits and recurrences will be&#xD;
      recorded.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
